WEBVTT

00:05:58.144 --> 00:06:01.234
Kwa nini tusifundishwe 
visa vya hao wanawake?

00:06:01.254 --> 00:06:03.624
Kwa nini wanawake wapewe vyeo
vilivyotoka

00:06:03.626 --> 00:06:06.636
zama zilizotangulia mafunzo ya dini yetu?

00:06:06.636 --> 00:06:09.286
Na kwa nini, kama sisi sote tuko sawasawa 
machoni mwa Mungu,

00:06:09.296 --> 00:06:11.966
hatuko sawasawa machoni mwa binadamu?

00:06:12.693 --> 00:06:17.043
Hayo yalinipeleka kufikiria mafunzo 
yangu ya utotoni.

00:06:18.232 --> 00:06:22.052
Anayeamua, na kuwa na mamlaka 
juu ya ujumbe,

00:06:22.082 --> 00:06:24.702
anayo nafasi kwenye meza,

00:06:24.722 --> 00:06:29.484
na kwa bahati mbaya, katika dini zote
za kidunia,

00:06:29.494 --> 00:06:31.092
hao si wanawake.